data.value: Coca-Cola® is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites. Have you ever wondered, is Coke® at McDonald’s different? Visit our Why Does McDonalds Coca Cola Taste So Good FAQ to find out. Enjoy a refreshing Coke® at McDonald’s in extra small, small, medium and large for $1 on the $1 $2 $3 Dollar Menu.
